article.description: — Zach Nutall had 24 points and Demarkus Lampley added 21 as Sam Houston State beat Rice 82-69 on Saturday.
article.headline: Nutall lifts Sam Houston State over Rice 82-69
article.linkText: Nutall lifts Sam Houston State over Rice 82-69
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- — Zach Nutall had 24 points and Demarkus Lampley added 21 as Sam Houston State beat Rice 82-69 on Saturday. Jarren Cook had 12 points for Sam Houston State (4-5). Bryce Monroe added 11 points. Quincy Olivari had 17 points for the Owls (5-2). Chris Mullins added 15 points and Travis Evee had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
